title: Forza Horizon
description: The Games on Demand version supports French, Spanish, Portuguese, English. Download the manual for this game by locating the game on http://marketplace.xbox.com and selecting “See Game Manual".  Where cars belong! Celebrate speed, music, and style at the Horizon Festival. From the makers of the highest-rated racing franchise of this generation, Forza Horizon combines legendary Forza authenticity with the freedom of the open road.

contentRating.label: T (Teen)
disclaimers: Online Interactions Not Rated by the ESRB

childDownloads.title: 1000 Club Expansion Pack
childDownloads.description: Free download! This game expansion adds fun new challenges for every car available to drive in Forza Horizon, over 1000 challenges in all! Every completed challenge awards you a gold medal. The more medals you collect, the faster you dominate friends on the new 1000 Club leaderboard. Do you have what it takes to reach 1000? Download today!

childDownloads.title: 1000 Club Expansion Pack Trailer
childDownloads.description: The Horizon Festival just got bigger! Check out the trailer for the Forza Horizon 1000 Club Expansion Pack, a FREE expansion featuring new challenges for every car in the game, more than 1,000 challenges in all! The expansion pack also includes 10 achievements worth 250 gamerscore and two new cars: the 1956 Ford F100 and the 1995 RUF CTR2.  Download the pack on April 16 for FREE, only on Xbox LIVE! For more information, see www.forzamotorsport.net.
